title: Last Days of the Universe Adult Sci-Fi Visual Novel WIP
description:
Welcome to a science-fiction universe for adults. 

A super-massive black-hole is continuously expanding in the center of a universe on the verge of collapse. Entire civilizations have been destroyed, others have escaped... for a while. No one is safe.

You are the leader (female (or male) depending on the Patreon support) of a world facing obliteration. Will you find a way to escape the impending doom?

Game for Windows

Currently in development. It currently has about 10-15 minutes of gameplay
